  <data key="d9">"Java class cargo repository located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.cargo. Uses related classes cargo, tracking id. Defines methods find, get all, next tracking id, store."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CargoRepository class is responsible for managing Cargo objects, providing operations to store and retrieve them, as well as managing TrackingId instances. It offers methods to find, retrieve all, and generate the next tracking ID."</data>
