  <data key="d9">"Java class tracking id located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.cargo. Implements interfaces tracking id, value object. Uses related classes tracking id. Defines methods equals, hash code, id string, same value as, to string, tracking id."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The TrackingId class is responsible for managing a unique tracking identifier, providing operations to compare and represent its value. It is a ValueObject, indicating it has no mutable state."</data>
