  <data key="d9">"Java class cargo tracking controller located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.tracking. Uses related classes cargo, cargo repository, cargo tracking view adapter, handling event repository, track command, track command validator, tracking id. Defines methods cargo tracking controller, index, on submit."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CargoTrackingController class is responsible for managing cargo tracking operations, providing methods to handle user input and submit tracking commands. It appears to interact with related classes to retrieve and update cargo information, validate tracking commands, and adapt view data."</data>
