  <data key="d9">"Java class handling event repository located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.handling. Uses related classes handling event, handling history, tracking id. Defines methods lookup handling history of cargo, store."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The HandlingEventRepository class is responsible for managing handling events and histories, providing operations to store and retrieve handling history of a cargo based on its tracking ID."</data>
