  <data key="d9">"Java class track command located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.tracking. Defines methods get tracking id, set tracking id, to string."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The TrackCommand class is responsible for managing a tracking ID, providing methods to retrieve and update it, and offering a string representation of its state. It appears to be a simple data container for tracking information."</data>
