<node id="class:se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.tracking.CargoTrackingViewAdapter">
  <data key="d0">"class:se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.tracking.CargoTrackingViewAdapter"</data>
  <data key="d1">"CargoTrackingViewAdapter"</data>
  <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
  <data key="d3">""</data>
  <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
  <data key="d5">{}</data>
  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class cargo tracking view adapter located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.tracking. Uses related classes cargo, delivery, handling activity, handling event, handling event view adapter. Defines methods cargo tracking view adapter, get destination, get display text, get eta, get events, get next expected activity, get origin, get status text, get tracking id, is misdirected."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CargoTrackingViewAdapter class is responsible for managing the display of cargo tracking information, providing methods to retrieve and format relevant data such as tracking ID, origin, destination, status, and events."</data>
