  <data key="d9">"Java class cargo factory located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.cargo. Uses related classes cargo, cargo repository, location repository, route specification, tracking id, un locode. Defines methods cargo factory, create cargo."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CargoFactory class is responsible for creating Cargo objects, managing the creation process of cargo entities. It provides a method to create a Cargo object based on given specifications."</data>
