  <data key="d9">"Java class location repository located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.location. Uses related classes un locode. Defines methods find, get all, store."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The LocationRepository class is responsible for managing locations, providing operations to find, retrieve all, and store locations. It appears to interact with UnLocode, a related class, to perform these operations."</data>
