  <data key="d9">"Java class un locode located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.location. Implements interfaces un locode, value object. Uses related classes un locode. Defines methods equals, hash code, id string, same value as, to string, un locode."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The UnLocode class is responsible for managing a unique location code, providing operations for comparison and string representation. It is a ValueObject, indicating it has no mutable state."</data>
