  <data key="d9">"Java class route specification located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.cargo. Inherits from abstract specification, itinerary. Implements interfaces route specification, value object. Uses related classes itinerary, route specification. Defines methods arrival deadline, destination, equals, hash code, is satisfied by, origin, route specification, same value as."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The RouteSpecification class is a ValueObject that represents a route specification, managing its origin, destination, and arrival deadline. It provides operations to check if it is satisfied by a given Itinerary and to compare itself with other RouteSpecifications."</data>
