<node id="class:se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.cargo.Leg">
  <data key="d0">"class:se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.cargo.Leg"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Leg"</data>
  <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
  <data key="d3">"Clase Leg"</data>
  <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
  <data key="d5">{"archivo": "monoliths/cargo/Leg.java"}</data>
  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class leg located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.cargo. Implements interfaces leg, value object. Uses related classes leg, voyage. Defines methods equals, hash code, leg, load location, load time, same value as, unload location, unload time, voyage."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The Leg class is responsible for managing the details of a cargo leg, including its load and unload locations and times, and its associated voyage. It provides operations to access and compare these details."</data>
