  <data key="d9">"Java class voyage located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.voyage. Implements interfaces domain entity, voyage. Uses related classes carrier movement, schedule, voyage, voyage number. Defines methods equals, hash code, same identity as, schedule, to string, voyage, voyage number."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The Voyage class is responsible for managing a domain entity representing a voyage, providing operations to schedule and identify the voyage by its number."</data>
