  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class handling report located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.handling.ws. Defines methods get completion time, get tracking ids, get type, get un locode, get voyage number, handling report, set completion time, set tracking ids, set type, set un locode, set voyage number."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The HandlingReport class is responsible for managing a report's details, providing getter and setter methods for its attributes such as completion time, tracking IDs, type, UN/LOCODE, and voyage number."</data>
