  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class itinerary located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.cargo. Implements interfaces itinerary, value object. Uses related classes handling event, itinerary, leg. Defines methods equals, final arrival date, final arrival location, hash code, initial departure location, is expected, itinerary, last leg, legs, same value as."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The Itinerary class is responsible for managing a sequence of cargo legs, providing operations to access and compare its state. It represents a collection of legs in a cargo journey."</data>
