  <data key="d9">"Java class handling event located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.handling. Implements interfaces domain event, handling event. Uses related classes cargo, handling event, voyage. Defines methods cargo, completion time, equals, handling event, hash code, id, location, registration time, same event as, to string, type, voyage."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The HandlingEvent class is responsible for managing handling events, providing access to its attributes such as id, type, cargo, location, registration time, completion time, and voyage, as well as comparing it with other events."</data>
