  <data key="d9">"Java class transit edge located in package com.pathfinder.api. Defines methods get edge, get from date, get from node, get to date, get to node, transit edge."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The TransitEdge class is responsible for managing a transit edge, providing access to its properties such as edge, from date, from node, to date, and to node. It offers a constructor method and getter methods for these properties."</data>
