<node id="class:se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.facade.internal.assembler.ItineraryCandidateDTOAssembler">
  <data key="d0">"class:se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.facade.internal.assembler.ItineraryCandidateDTOAssembler"</data>
  <data key="d1">"ItineraryCandidateDTOAssembler"</data>
  <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
  <data key="d3">"Clase ItineraryCandidateDTOAssembler"</data>
  <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
  <data key="d5">{"archivo": "monoliths/cargo/ItineraryCandidateDTOAssembler.java"}</data>
  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class itinerary candidate dtoassembler located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.facade.internal.assembler. Uses related classes itinerary, leg, leg dto, location repository, route candidate dto, un locode, voyage, voyage number, voyage repository. Defines methods from dto, to dto, to leg dto."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The ItineraryCandidateDTOAssembler class is responsible for converting between Itinerary and RouteCandidateDTO objects, as well as their constituent parts, such as Legs and Locations. It provides methods to assemble and disassemble these objects."</data>
