  <data key="d9">"Java class route candidate dto located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.facade.dto. Uses related classes leg dto. Defines methods get legs, route candidate dto."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The RouteCandidateDTO class is responsible for managing route candidates, providing a representation of a route candidate and its associated legs. It offers operations to access the legs of a route candidate."</data>
