  <data key="d9">"Java class leg dto located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.facade.dto. Defines methods get from, get load time, get to, get unload time, get voyage number, leg dto."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The LegDTO class is responsible for managing information about a leg of a journey, providing access to its attributes such as departure and arrival locations, load and unload times, and voyage number. It offers getter methods to retrieve these attributes."</data>
