  <data key="d9">"Java class voyage number located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.voyage. Implements interfaces value object, voyage number. Uses related classes voyage number. Defines methods equals, hash code, id string, same value as, to string, voyage number."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The VoyageNumber class is responsible for managing unique voyage identifiers, providing operations for comparison and string representation. It is a ValueObject, implying it has no mutable state."</data>
