  <data key="d9">"Java class cargo admin controller located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.web. Uses related classes booking service facade, cargo routing dto, leg dto, registration command, route assignment command, route candidate dto. Defines methods assign itinerary, cargo admin controller, change destination, init binder, list, pick new destination, register, registration, select itinerary, show."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CargoAdminController class is responsible for managing cargo-related operations, providing methods for listing, assigning itineraries, changing destinations, and registering cargo. It appears to interact with the BookingServiceFacade to perform these operations."</data>
