<node id="class:se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.facade.BookingServiceFacade">
  <data key="d0">"class:se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.facade.BookingServiceFacade"</data>
  <data key="d1">"BookingServiceFacade"</data>
  <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
  <data key="d3">""</data>
  <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
  <data key="d5">{}</data>
  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class booking service facade located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.facade. Uses related classes cargo routing dto, location dto, route candidate dto. Defines methods assign cargo to route, book new cargo, change destination, list all cargos, list shipping locations, load cargo for routing, request possible routes for cargo."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The BookingServiceFacade class is responsible for managing bookings and cargo routing operations, providing methods to assign cargo to routes, book new cargo, and retrieve lists of cargos and shipping locations. It offers various operations to manipulate cargo and route information, including loading cargo for routing and requesting possible routes for a given cargo."</data>
