  <data key="d9">"Java class registration command located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.web. Defines methods get arrival deadline, get destination unlocode, get origin unlocode, set arrival deadline, set destination unlocode, set origin unlocode."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The RegistrationCommand class is responsible for managing booking registration data, providing operations to set and retrieve origin and destination unlocodes, as well as an arrival deadline. It appears to encapsulate the data necessary for a registration command in a web-based booking system."</data>
