  <data key="d9">"Java class cargo routing dto located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.facade.dto. Uses related classes leg dto. Defines methods add leg, cargo routing dto, get arrival deadline, get final destination, get legs, get origin, get tracking id, is misrouted, is routed."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CargoRoutingDTO class is responsible for managing cargo routing information, encapsulating data such as origin, destination, tracking ID, and legs of the journey. It provides operations to add legs, retrieve routing details, and check routing status."</data>
