  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class route assignment command located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.web. Uses related classes leg command. Defines methods get legs, get tracking id, set legs, set tracking id."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The RouteAssignmentCommand class is responsible for managing route assignments, providing operations to set and retrieve legs and tracking IDs. It appears to be a part of a web-based booking system, possibly handling commands related to route assignments."</data>
