  <data key="d9">"Java class handling event registration attempt consumer located in package se.citerus.dddsample.infrastructure.messaging.jms. Uses related classes handling event registration attempt, handling event service. Defines methods handling event registration attempt consumer, on message."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer class is responsible for managing event registration attempts, specifically handling incoming messages related to these attempts. It provides the onMessage operation to process incoming messages."</data>
