  <data key="d9">"Java class cargo inspection service located in package se.citerus.dddsample.application. Uses related classes tracking id. Defines methods inspect cargo."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CargoInspectionService class is responsible for managing cargo inspections, providing the inspectCargo operation to perform inspections. It likely interacts with TrackingId to identify the cargo being inspected."</data>
