  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class cargo handled consumer located in package se.citerus.dddsample.infrastructure.messaging.jms. Uses related classes cargo inspection service, tracking id. Defines methods cargo handled consumer, on message."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CargoHandledConsumer class is responsible for handling cargo-related messages, specifically managing the receipt and processing of messages related to cargo inspections. It provides an onMessage operation to handle incoming messages."</data>
