  <data key="d9">"Java class application events located in package se.citerus.dddsample.application. Uses related classes cargo, handling event, handling event registration attempt. Defines methods cargo has arrived, cargo was handled, cargo was misdirected, received handling event registration attempt."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The ApplicationEvents class is responsible for managing application-level events related to cargo handling, such as arrival, handling, and misdirection. It provides methods to notify these events and handle registration attempts for handling events."</data>
