  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class jms application events impl located in package se.citerus.dddsample.infrastructure.messaging.jms. Implements interfaces application events. Uses related classes cargo, handling event, handling event registration attempt. Defines methods cargo has arrived, cargo was handled, cargo was misdirected, jms application events impl, received handling event registration attempt."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The JmsApplicationEventsImpl class is responsible for managing JMS application events, specifically handling events related to cargo arrival, handling, misdirection, and handling event registration attempts. It provides operations to notify these events."</data>
