  <data key="d9">"Java class cargo tracking rest service located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.tracking.ws. Uses related classes cargo, cargo repository, cargo tracking dto, handling event repository, tracking id. Defines methods cargo tracking rest service, track cargo."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CargoTrackingRestService class is responsible for managing cargo tracking operations, providing a REST interface to track cargo. It likely interacts with other classes to retrieve and update cargo information."</data>
