<node id="class:se.citerus.dddsample.application.BookingService">
  <data key="d0">"class:se.citerus.dddsample.application.BookingService"</data>
  <data key="d1">"BookingService"</data>
  <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
  <data key="d3">""</data>
  <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
  <data key="d5">{}</data>
  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class booking service located in package se.citerus.dddsample.application. Uses related classes itinerary, tracking id, un locode. Defines methods assign cargo to route, book new cargo, change destination, request possible routes for cargo."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The BookingService class is responsible for managing bookings and cargo assignments, providing operations to book new cargo, assign cargo to routes, change destinations, and request possible routes for cargo. It appears to interact with related classes such as Itinerary, TrackingId, and UnLocode."</data>
