  <data key="d9">"Java class booking service facade impl located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.facade.internal. Implements interfaces booking service facade. Uses related classes booking service, cargo, cargo repository, cargo routing dto, cargo routing dtoassembler, itinerary, itinerary candidate dtoassembler, location dto, location dtoassembler, location repository, route candidate dto, tracking id, un locode, voyage repository. Defines methods assign cargo to route, book new cargo, booking service facade impl, change destination, list all cargos, list shipping locations, load cargo for routing, request possible routes for cargo."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The BookingServiceFacadeImpl class is responsible for managing bookings and cargo routing operations, providing methods to assign cargo to routes, book new cargo, change destinations, and list all cargos and shipping locations. It appears to act as a facade for the BookingService, encapsulating its functionality and offering a simplified interface for interacting with cargo and route data."</data>
