  <data key="d9">"Java class upload directory scanner located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.handling.file. Uses related classes application events, handling event, handling event registration attempt, tracking id, un locode, voyage number. Defines methods after properties set, delete, move, parse, parse line, queue attempt, run, to rejected filename, upload directory scanner, write rejected lines to file."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The UploadDirectoryScanner class is responsible for managing file uploads and handling related operations, such as parsing, moving, and deleting files. It provides methods for processing uploaded files and writing rejected lines to a file."</data>
