<node id="class:se.citerus.dddsample.application.impl.BookingServiceImpl">
  <data key="d0">"class:se.citerus.dddsample.application.impl.BookingServiceImpl"</data>
  <data key="d1">"BookingServiceImpl"</data>
  <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
  <data key="d3">"Clase BookingServiceImpl"</data>
  <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
  <data key="d5">{"archivo": "monoliths/cargo/BookingServiceImpl.java"}</data>
  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class booking service impl located in package se.citerus.dddsample.application.impl. Implements interfaces booking service. Uses related classes cargo, cargo factory, cargo repository, itinerary, location repository, route specification, routing service, tracking id, un locode. Defines methods assign cargo to route, book new cargo, booking service impl, change destination, request possible routes for cargo."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The BookingServiceImpl class is responsible for managing bookings of cargo, providing operations to book new cargo, assign cargo to routes, change destinations, and request possible routes for cargo. It appears to interact with various related classes to facilitate these operations."</data>
