  <data key="d9">"Java class routing service located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.service. Uses related classes itinerary, route specification. Defines methods fetch routes for specification."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The RoutingService class is responsible for managing routes and providing operations to fetch routes based on a given specification. It appears to be a service that retrieves routes for a specific itinerary or route specification."</data>
