  <data key="d9">"Java class handling event factory located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.handling. Uses related classes cannot create handling event exception, cargo, cargo repository, handling event, location repository, tracking id, un locode, unknown cargo exception, unknown location exception, unknown voyage exception, voyage, voyage number, voyage repository. Defines methods create handling event, find cargo, find location, find voyage, handling event factory."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The HandlingEventFactory class is responsible for managing HandlingEvent instances and providing operations to create them based on related cargo, location, and voyage information. It appears to act as a factory for creating HandlingEvent objects, utilizing data from Cargo, Location, and Voyage repositories."</data>
