  <data key="d9">"Java class handling history located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.handling. Implements interfaces handling history, value object. Uses related classes handling event, handling history, tracking id. Defines methods distinct events by completion time, equals, filter on cargo, handling history, hash code, most recently completed event, same value as."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The HandlingHistory class is responsible for managing a collection of handling events, providing operations to filter and retrieve specific events based on their completion time and cargo. It appears to be a Value Object, as indicated by its package and method names, and is likely used to represent a sequence of handling events."</data>
