  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class pathfinder application context located in package com.pathfinder.config. Uses related classes graph dao, graph daostub, graph traversal service, graph traversal service impl. Defines methods graph dao, graph traversal service."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The PathfinderApplicationContext class is responsible for managing the application context, specifically providing access to a graph data access object (DAO) and a graph traversal service."</data>
