  <data key="d9">"Java class graph traversal service located in package com.pathfinder.api. Uses related classes transit path. Defines methods find shortest path."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The GraphTraversalService class is responsible for managing graph traversal operations, specifically providing a method to find the shortest path. It likely operates on a graph data structure, possibly in conjunction with the TransitPath class."</data>
