  <data key="d9">"Java class graph traversal service impl located in package com.pathfinder.internal. Implements interfaces graph traversal service. Uses related classes graph dao, transit edge, transit path. Defines methods find shortest path, get random chunk of nodes, get random number of candidates, graph traversal service impl, next date."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The GraphTraversalServiceImpl class is responsible for managing graph traversal operations, providing methods to find shortest paths, retrieve random node chunks, and generate random candidate numbers, as well as handling date-related logic. It likely interacts with graph data storage and traversal services to perform these operations."</data>
