  <data key="d9">"Java class abstract specification located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.shared. Implements interfaces specification. Uses related classes and specification, not specification, or specification, specification. Defines methods and, is satisfied by, not, or."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The AbstractSpecification class is responsible for managing logical specifications, providing operations to combine them through logical AND, OR, and NOT operations. It defines a base interface for creating complex specifications from simpler ones."</data>
