  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class and specification located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.shared. Inherits from abstract specification. Uses related classes specification. Defines methods and specification, is satisfied by."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The AndSpecification class is responsible for managing a combination of specifications, providing a way to evaluate whether all related specifications are satisfied. It likely extends or implements the AbstractSpecification or Specification classes."</data>
