  <data key="d9">"Java class or specification located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.shared. Inherits from abstract specification. Uses related classes specification. Defines methods is satisfied by, or specification."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The OrSpecification class is responsible for managing a combination of specifications, allowing it to determine if any of the individual specifications are satisfied. It provides operations to create instances and check if a given input satisfies the combined specification."</data>
