  <data key="d9">"Java class not specification located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.shared. Inherits from abstract specification. Uses related classes specification. Defines methods is satisfied by, not specification."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The NotSpecification class is responsible for managing a specification, providing a way to negate its satisfaction. It offers operations to create a NotSpecification instance and check if a given object satisfies the negated specification."</data>
