  <data key="d9">"Java class handling event repository jpa located in package se.citerus.dddsample.infrastructure.persistence.jpa. Inherits from handling event, handling event repository. Uses related classes handling event, handling history, tracking id. Defines methods get handling history of cargo, lookup handling history of cargo, store."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The HandlingEventRepositoryJPA class is responsible for managing handling history data, specifically providing operations to retrieve and store handling events associated with tracking IDs. It appears to be a data access component for handling event data in a JPA (Java Persistence API) context."</data>
