  <data key="d9">"Java class cargo tracking dto located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.tracking.ws. Uses related classes handling event dto. Defines methods cargo tracking dto."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CargoTrackingDTO class is responsible for managing cargo tracking data, providing a data transfer object (DTO) for storing and exchanging cargo tracking information. It likely offers a constructor or initialization method to create a new instance with relevant tracking data."</data>
