  <data key="d9">"Java class leg command located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.web. Defines methods get from date, get from un locode, get to date, get to un locode, get voyage number, set from date, set from un locode, set to date, set to un locode, set voyage number."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The LegCommand class is responsible for managing voyage-related data, specifically for a leg of a journey, and provides getter and setter operations for its attributes. It encapsulates information such as from date, from location, to date, to location, and voyage number."</data>
