<node id="class:se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.handling.UnknownCargoException">
  <data key="d0">"class:se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.handling.UnknownCargoException"</data>
  <data key="d1">"UnknownCargoException"</data>
  <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
  <data key="d3">"Clase UnknownCargoException"</data>
  <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
  <data key="d5">{"archivo": "monoliths/cargo/UnknownCargoException.java"}</data>
  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class unknown cargo exception located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.handling. Inherits from cannot create handling event exception. Uses related classes tracking id. Defines methods get message, unknown cargo exception."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The UnknownCargoException class is responsible for managing unknown cargo-related exceptions in the domain model, providing a way to retrieve a message describing the exception."</data>
