  <data key="d9">"Java class location repository jpa located in package se.citerus.dddsample.infrastructure.persistence.jpa. Inherits from location repository. Uses related classes un locode. Defines methods find, find by un lo code, get all, store."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The LocationRepositoryJPA class is responsible for managing locations, providing operations to find, retrieve, and store location data. It appears to be a data access object for a Java Persistence API (JPA) implementation, interacting with a database to perform CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations on locations."</data>
