  <data key="d9">"Java class voyage repository jpa located in package se.citerus.dddsample.infrastructure.persistence.jpa. Inherits from voyage, voyage repository. Uses related classes voyage, voyage number. Defines methods find, find by voyage number, store."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The VoyageRepositoryJPA class is responsible for managing Voyage objects, providing operations to find and store them, and possibly retrieving Voyages by their unique identifier, VoyageNumber. It is likely a data access object for a Java Persistence API (JPA) implementation."</data>
