  <data key="d9">"Java class handling event view adapter located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.tracking. Uses related classes handling event, voyage. Defines methods get description, get location, get time, get type, get voyage number, handling event view adapter, is expected."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The HandlingEventViewAdapter class is responsible for managing a HandlingEvent object, providing access to its attributes such as description, location, time, type, voyage number, and expected status. It offers methods to retrieve these attributes."</data>
