  <data key="d9">"Java class delivery located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.cargo. Implements interfaces delivery, value object. Uses related classes delivery, handling activity, handling event, handling history, itinerary, leg, route specification, voyage. Defines methods calculate current voyage, calculate eta, calculate last known location, calculate misdirection status, calculate next expected activity, calculate routing status, calculate transport status, calculate unloaded at destination, calculated at, current voyage, delivery, derived from, equals, estimated time of arrival, hash code, is misdirected, is unloaded at destination, last known location, next expected activity, on track, routing status, same value as, transport status, update on routing."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The Delivery class is responsible for managing the state of a cargo delivery, providing methods to calculate and retrieve various status and location information. It appears to be a Value Object, encapsulating the state of a delivery and offering operations to derive its current status and location."</data>
