  <data key="d9">"Java class handling activity located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.cargo. Implements interfaces handling activity, value object. Uses related classes handling activity, handling event, voyage. Defines methods equals, handling activity, hash code, location, same value as, type, voyage."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The HandlingActivity class is responsible for managing cargo handling activities, providing operations to access and compare its location, type, and voyage. It is a ValueObject, indicating that it represents a unique set of values."</data>
