  <data key="d9">"Java class carrier movement located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.voyage. Implements interfaces carrier movement, value object. Uses related classes carrier movement. Defines methods arrival location, arrival time, carrier movement, departure location, departure time, equals, hash code, same value as."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CarrierMovement class is responsible for managing the details of a carrier movement, including its departure and arrival locations and times, and provides operations to compare and verify its value."</data>
