  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class sample data generator located in package se.citerus.dddsample.infrastructure.sampledata. Uses related classes cargo, cargo repository, handling event, handling event factory, handling event repository, handling history, itinerary, leg, location repository, route specification, tracking id, voyage repository. Defines methods generate, get base time stamp, load hibernate data, offset, sample data generator, ts."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The SampleDataGenerator class is responsible for generating sample data, likely for testing or demonstration purposes, and provides methods to manipulate and retrieve this data. It appears to be designed to work with various domain classes, such as Cargo, HandlingEvent, and Itinerary."</data>
