  <data key="d9">"Java class cargo tracking dtoconverter located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.tracking.ws. Uses related classes cargo, cargo tracking dto, delivery, handling activity, handling event, handling event dto. Defines methods convert, convert description, convert destination, convert eta, convert handling events, convert is expected, convert is misdirected, convert location, convert next expected activity, convert status text, convert time, convert tracking id, convert type, convert voyage number."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CargoTrackingDTOConverter class is responsible for converting Cargo and related objects into CargoTrackingDTO objects, providing a mapping between the two data structures. It offers a set of conversion methods for specific properties of the Cargo and related objects."</data>
