  <data key="d9">"Java class cargo repository jpa located in package se.citerus.dddsample.infrastructure.persistence.jpa. Inherits from cargo, cargo repository. Uses related classes cargo, tracking id. Defines methods find, find by tracking id, get all, next tracking id, next tracking id string, store."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The CargoRepositoryJPA class is responsible for managing Cargo objects in a database, providing operations to store, retrieve, and query Cargos by tracking ID. It offers methods to interact with the database, including storing and retrieving Cargos, as well as generating new tracking IDs."</data>
