  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class dddsample application context located in package se.citerus.dddsample.config. Uses related classes application events, booking service, booking service impl, cargo factory, cargo inspection service, cargo inspection service impl, cargo repository, external routing service, graph traversal service, handling event factory, handling event repository, handling event service, handling event service impl, location repository, routing service, sample data generator, voyage repository. Defines methods booking service, cargo factory, cargo inspection service, handling event factory, handling event service, routing service, sample data generator."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The DDDSampleApplicationContext class is responsible for managing a set of services and factories, providing access to them through its methods. It appears to be a container or registry for various domain-specific services and utilities."</data>
