  <data key="d9">"Java class location dtoassembler located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.booking.facade.internal.assembler. Uses related classes location dto. Defines methods to dto, to dtolist."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The LocationDTOAssembler class is responsible for assembling data transfer objects (DTOs) related to locations, providing methods to convert domain objects into LocationDTOs and collections of domain objects into lists of LocationDTOs."</data>
