<node id="class:se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.handling.HandlingReportParser">
  <data key="d0">"class:se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.handling.HandlingReportParser"</data>
  <data key="d1">"HandlingReportParser"</data>
  <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
  <data key="d3">"Clase HandlingReportParser"</data>
  <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
  <data key="d5">{"archivo": "monoliths/cargo/HandlingReportParser.java"}</data>
  <data key="d6">[]</data>
  <data key="d7">false</data>
  <data key="d8">null</data>
  <data key="d9">"Java class handling report parser located in package se.citerus.dddsample.interfaces.handling. Uses related classes handling event, handling event registration attempt, handling report, tracking id, un locode, voyage number. Defines methods parse, parse completion time, parse date, parse event type, parse tracking id, parse tracking ids, parse un locode, parse voyage number."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The HandlingReportParser class is responsible for parsing HandlingReport data, providing methods to extract specific information such as tracking IDs, completion times, dates, event types, and voyage numbers. It manages the conversion of HandlingReport data into a structured format."</data>
