  <data key="d9">"Java class builder located in package se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.voyage. Uses related classes builder, carrier movement, schedule, voyage, voyage number. Defines methods add movement, build, builder."</data>
  <data key="d10">"The Builder class is responsible for constructing a Voyage object, providing methods to add movements and ultimately build the voyage."</data>
